ComicInfo.Summary:
The stunning might of Sieglinde and Battleship Zero is put to the test versus an enemy they will never see coming - the US Zephyr forces!
Available with Regular, Wraparound, War Crimes, Propaganda, and Blitzkrieg by series artist Daniel Gete, and a limited VIP Premium cover by Gabriel Andrade.
